Mike Starr (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mike_Starr_(actor) 0 Michael Starr (born July 29, 1950) is an American character actor. He is notable for his large size, standing 6 ft 3 ​1⁄2 in (192 cm) tall, and has typically been typecast as a thug or henchman. Michael_Starr ( born July_29_,_1950 ) is an_American_character_actor .
